Newest Filings











Alabama-Two Properties, LLC $3,350,000 Financing
Alabama-Two Properties, LLC just submitted form D announcing $3,350,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. Alabama-Two Properties, LLC was able to sell $3,350,000. That is 100% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $3,350,000. The financing was made by 44 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $25,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-11-17. Alabama-Two Properties, LLC is based in  C/O NIGRO KARLIN SEGAL & FELDSTEIN, LLP 10960 WILSHIRE BLVD., 5TH FLOOR LOS ANGELES 90025. The firm's business is Other Real Estate. The firm's revenue range is No Revenues. The form was signed by  Todd Okum.





